column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, el.ra, el.dec into mydb.MyTable_# from mydb.MyTable_# as el   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq( el.ra, el.dec, #) AS near    JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON s.specObjID = near.specObjID  WHERE  s.snMedian >= # AND  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=#
